July 28, 2017 11:35 PM ET
Wireless Telecommunication Services

Company Overview of Vodafone Group Services Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Vodafone Group Services Limited provides mobile communications products and services. The company was incorporated in 1999 and is based in Newbury, United Kingdom. Vodafone Group Services Limited operates as a subsidiary of Vodafone Group Public Limited Company.


Vodafone HouseThe ConnectionNewbury,  RG14 2FNUnited KingdomFounded in 1999



Phone: 44 01 6353 3251

Fax: 44 01 6354 5713








